title: ETKA 7 Updates (598 - 710)
description:
Updates Etka 7 from build 597 to 710.

   Step 1 - Unrar

   Step 2 - Open ETKA7 Updates directory

   Step 3 - You now have 4 folders that need to have the contents moved to
            the proper directory.

            Open & Move all files in each directory to the following paths.


            Audi.Updates.598-710    -> C:etkaDATAAUUpdate
            Seat.Updates.127-239    -> C:etkaDATASEUpdate
            Skoda.Updates.133-245   -> C:etkaDATASKUpdate
            VW.Updates.598-710      -> C:etkaDATASKUpdate

   Step 4 - Now comes the part where you will sit through a bunch of update
            installs. Please know in advance this will take aproximately about
            2 HOURS or more in time depending on your system and patience!

            Once you start the first update it will continue to install each
            update one after the other so be patient and install everything.

            ** The password you need to install is case sensitive so copy it
               exactly as shown below and paste it each time the updates ask
               you for it.  WHEN THE SETUP PROGRAM STYLE CHANGES, THE PASSWORD
	      ALSO CHANGES.

               Passwords: AKTEForum.TK
			  
		        avaf


            Go to C:etkaDATAAUUpdate

            Launch eupdAU598D.exe and continue the install until its
            finished and it will automatically launch etka.

            Close etka and restart it.

            You've now patched your etka release 7.0 from build 597 to 710.
